form_values.19ac: See access details, client excavated for services not knowing that knotweed is hidden in established vegetation. The result is new peppered growths along part of the trench route. Access to the original stand is difficult and hidden by other established vegetation.  Was owned by a renowned gardener Hicks. Shape and size of impacted area difficult to determine due to the presence of other vegetation. Recommend stem injection to mature plants, spray to trench area, cut back access to allow for treatment. Either burn or leave material on site, complete with first treatment visit. Complete hand rhizome aggravation in winter months in years on and two. Client currently does not need a mortgage.
